# Even Number Sum Calculator

## Project Goal
The goal of this project is to build a simple Python program that calculates the sum of two even numbers. This project helps beginners understand basic Python programming concepts such as variables, input, conditions, and arithmetic operations.

## Problem Statement
Many beginner programmers struggle to understand how to validate numbers and perform simple calculations using Python. This project solves that problem by creating a program that accepts two numbers from the user and calculates their sum only if they are even numbers.

